      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i was looking at some old maps of DC and some recent satellite imagery... is it just me or do the main avenues and the way the monuments are laid out look like they're forming a specific geometric shape? like, it almost looks intentional, not just for traffic but like a symbol or something. do u see the pattern too?",
